  "data": [
    [
      [
        "NO"
      ],
      [
        "As I finish talking, I notice that [Paul] was listening to me intently."
      ],
      [
        "[he] hadn't looked away all this time,"
      ],
      [
        "and had [his] beautiful purple eyes looking right into me. "
      ],
      [
        "I feel heat creep up to my cheeks as I become completely quiet and look away. "
      ],
      [
        "Huh? why so quiet all of a sudden? what’s wrong?"
      ],
      [
        "N-nothing, It's all good. "
      ],
      [
        "[Paul] then pushed me slightly with [his] shoulder and smirked at me."
      ],
      [
        "Hey, there's no shame in getting red as a cherry. "
      ],
      [
        "No, no, no, more like a tomato. HA HA!"
      ],
      [
        "My face is now full on red as I place my hands on my face, trying to hide my red ahh face."
      ],
      [
        "I'm gonna call you 'mato from now on!"
      ],
      [
        "Shut upppp."
      ],
      [
        "After that, we just keep eating. I manage to endure [Fabian]’s nagging as I"
      ],
      [
        "finish my hamburguer and [he] does too."
      ],
      [
        "We enjoy chatting a bit more, but ultimately need to go back to our houses to sleep well. "
      ],
      [
        "This was a very nice day… It started a bit off,"
      ],
      [
        "but now I can't even remember what I was sad about in the morning! "
      ],
      [
        "I arrive to my bed and plop myself down with my heart beating faster than ever. "
      ],
      [
        "Could it be that [Paul] is my one and only?"
      ],
      [
        "Two months had already passed so quickly… And [Paul] and I had been incredibly in love all this time. "
      ],
      [
        "I look up at [him] and recall all the time we had spent together."
      ],
      [
        "I remember our first encounter, our first kiss…"
      ],
      [
        "even all the times we’ve had fun going out to eat, or walking in the park."
      ],
      [
        "Sometimes we played videogames behind school, ooh!"
      ],
      [
        "and how could I forget when [he] tried on some silly hats on the mall! I still have the photos!"
      ],
      [
        "It's been the best two months of my life to be honest."
      ],
      [
        "It all felt as if I were in a dream that would never ever end- "
      ],
      [
        "Slap!"
      ],
      [
        "The back of [Paul]'s hand had slapped me on my arm. Pulling me away from my thoughts."
      ],
      [
        "Pay attention, will you? Remember the exam is tomorrow."
      ],
      [
        "Sorry…"
      ],
      [
        "Yeah… this was something that [Paul] had…"
      ],
      [
        "[he] usually got very moody whenever [he] saw me not paying attention."
      ],
      [
        "For some reason, the pain in my arm lingers a bit more than usual."
      ],
      [
        "The school bell rings and [Paul] gets up. I get up and quickly follow [him]. "
      ],
      [
        "Aah, I'm really craving some buffalo wings. Let's go."
      ],
      [
        "I just nod and keep up with [his] steps."
      ],
      [
        "My mind is absent as we silently walk towards our food spot. "
      ],
      [
        "I recall how excited I was in the morning… "
      ],
      [
        "It had been a nice time with [Paul], but [he] had this little detail…"
      ],
      [
        "now that I think about it, [he] had gotten more comfortable "
      ],
      [
        "with doing that stuff ever since the flick on the head."
      ],
      [
        "[Paul] and I arrive to the plaza and order our food."
      ],
      [
        "We then start eating. Halfway through my food, [Paul] clears [his] throat and looks at me."
      ],
      [
        "So… You've been awfully quiet today, [tn]. You alright?"
      ],
      [
        "I quickly gulp my food and nod."
      ],
      [
        "Y-yeah, yeah… It’s just… I’ve been thinking about the exam."
      ],
      [
        "I'm replaying the information in my head. "
      ],
      [
        "Oh! I see. Good! I’m glad to see you’re on the road for an A+."
      ],
      [
        "I nod and keep on eating."
      ],
      [
        "After a while, we both finish eating and decide to head our own separate ways. "
      ],
      [
        "I look at the stars as I walk, then, I arrive home."
      ],
      [
        "Helpie greets me, and I ask him to make me dinner as I go lay on my bed. "
      ],
      [
        "My heart aches terribly. I feel like not everything is as nice as before, but I can't really pinpoint what it is."
      ],
      [
        "My cheek becomes wet with very familiar salty drops as I turn to my side."
      ],
      [
        "But suddenly I whine. I look at my arm, and it's the spot where [Paul] had slapped me before…"
      ],
      [
        "a small bruise had formed in my arm. "
      ],
      [
        "It is a brand new day, I feel nervous as I sit on my desk."
      ],
      [
        "It is exam day after all! Still, I know I studied hard all week, and now I’m as sharp as a knife."
      ],
      [
        "I can do this! "
      ],
      [
        "[Paul] enters the classroom soon after, and sits next to me as usual."
      ],
      [
        "'Sup, Ready for the mid-term?"
      ],
      [
        "Yeah. I just want to get over with it."
      ],
      [
        "Well, just focus on getting an A+. Show me that I can work with you."
      ],
      [
        "I tilt my head and open my mouth to ask [him] what [he] meant by that,"
      ],
      [
        "but our teacher interrupts us to ask us to open our devices and do the exam. "
      ],
      [
        "I tremble a little bit as I look at the start button, but I exhale, trusting what I know. "
      ],
      [
        "It takes me like 15 minutes to finish it."
      ],
      [
        "There were only a few questions where I doubted my answers but I was confident nonetheless."
      ],
      [
        "I look at [Paul], and [he] had already finished."
      ],
      [
        "That was actually kind of impressive. "
      ],
      [
        "10 minutes passed, and everybody was finished,"
      ],
      [
        "so we were able to check our exam’s grade. "
      ],
      [
        "I open the review tab, and my grade is A."
      ],
      [
        "Yes! I throw my fists in the air, celebrating my accomplishment. "
      ],
      [
        "[Paul] leans in to see my screen. "
      ],
      [
        "What did you ge-"
      ],
      [
        "wait… an A? Really? And you’re celebrating? "
      ],
      [
        "Huh? But It's an A, It’s good."
      ],
      [
        "I told you. A. PLUS."
      ],
      [
        "And look, you failed such an easy question. Ugh."
      ],
      [
        "My excitedness dies down as I look at my A once again."
      ],
      [
        "I studied a lot for this, but… It’s just not an A +. "
      ],
      [
        "I look over at [Paul] and see he actually got the highest score."
      ],
      [
        "My heart begins to sulk. It seems that I always fall short at what I want to do and accomplish."
      ],
      [
        "But… did [he] really have to say it like that?"
      ],
      [
        "[tn], how about we go for some instant noodles today? I’m starving. "
      ],
      [
        "[Paul]'s question threw me off, snapping me out of my thoughts. "
      ],
      [
        "Um… I don't know, I'm not really in the mood for that."
      ],
      [
        "C'mon, come with me. I don't want to eat alone."
      ],
      [
        "I tilt my head and nod, letting [Paul] lead the way."
      ],
      [
        "It is a quiet walk once more, and [Paul] doesn't seem to mind as [he] whistles carelessly. "
      ],
      [
        "My heart beats fast, and my stomach feels heavy all the way."
      ],
      [
        "I need to tell [him] how I really feel."
      ],
      [
        "We arrive at the convenience store and make our noodles."
      ],
      [
        "We sit from across each other and I wait for my noodles to cool down as my lip quivers. "
      ],
      [
        "I can't pass this opportunity, I need to let [Paul] know that I don’t like how [he]'s treating me."
      ],
      [
        "[Paul], listen. These two months have been amazing with you, we've done so much things and laughed."
      ],
      [
        "But I need to tell you that you have been… very mean to me lately."
      ],
      [
        "And I know, I may annoy you sometimes, and I may not be as brilliant as you,"
      ],
      [
        "but I don't think I deserve to be treated like this…"
      ],
      [
        "your mean words, your slaps and, it’s just…"
      ],
      [
        "I don't feel good with this at all. I don’t like it "
      ],
      [
        "[Paul] slurps the noodle that [he] had in [his] mouth and clears [his] throat."
      ],
      [
        "Uh… wait, are you being for real right now? "
      ],
      [
        "Yes! [Paul], I don't like how you treat me sometimes!"
      ],
      [
        "[Paul]'s eyes widen and [he] places [his] empty cup of noodles on the table."
      ],
      [
        "[tn], I had no idea that you felt like this…"
      ],
      [
        " I'm sorry, If you don't like it, I promise I’ll never treat you like that again, okay?"
      ],
      [
        " It's just that I thought that was a good way to show you how much I care about you, and want you to improve…"
      ],
      [
        " To be honest, you get too distracted in class, and I worry that you’ll do badly in tests or projects…"
      ],
      [
        "[tn], I'm sorry, I won't do it again, I promise."
      ],
      [
        "I nod and look to the side. Even if he apologized, I feel like something is still bugging me."
      ]
    ],
